      "content": "hey so im looking at my insulin for tonight. i barely ate anything for dinner, like just a few bites of salad. my sugar is pretty stable right now so im thinking of just skipping my basal dose tonight so i dont crash in my sleep. is that actually fine to do if i didnt eat much?",
